The paper deals with signal reconstruction using compressive sensing (CS) with side information (SI), which is a topic that falls under the information theory (cs.IT) sub-category. The use of adaptive weights and the application of the proposed algorithm to multiview image databases suggest that the paper may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), multimedia (cs.MM), and signal processing (cs.SI) sub-categories.
